  "id": "RAW_191a24f8",
  "title": "苹果“云上谷歌”，连 Siri 都不放过",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mjc1NjM3MjY2MA==&mid=2691565353&idx=1&sn=3225c9cf27baaa166325fe5ffdd49b16",
  "date": "2026-03-03 03:29:00",
  "author": "腾讯科技",
  "siteName": "腾讯科技",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;text-align:justify;margin-right:8px;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.562\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1000\" style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;border: 0px none;width: 100%;max-width: 100%;border-radius: 4px;display: inline-block;aspect-ratio: 1.78056 / 1;\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"325\" data-imgfileid=\"544081697\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=dc0a501d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FQmK3dYQtkw2dsEYlJIG3Fmm8WXoWLa9Zyqv86LjlExia25U9fXFyCshtF0cD1R4iaAoic3x2O5ExJj4NyY4ULTtA4KfMRbaomNOspiauog93tWs%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">躺在谷歌云上的库克。图片由AI生成</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:right;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 8px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><strong style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;font-weight: bolder;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">文丨苏扬</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:right;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><strong style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;font-weight: bolder;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">编辑丨徐青阳</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">苹果可能要把最核心产品之一的Siri，送到谷歌数据中心“寄养”了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">近日，据知情人士透露，为了能让即将推出的、由AI大模型驱动的新版Siri顺利跑起来，苹果正在认真考虑一个方案：</span></span><strong style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;font-weight: bolder;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">让谷歌在其数据中心里专门划出一片区域，架设服务器来运行Siri。</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">苹果的动作和此前的布局，形成了巨大的反差。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">2024年苹果就高调发布“苹果智能”（Apple Intelligence）套件，包括自研的“私有云计算”系统——采用自研芯片的苹果服务器来处理用户的复杂AI请求，以此保护隐私。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><strong style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;font-weight: bolder;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">一位前员工透露，“苹果云”实际运行得并不理想，上线后使用率仅为10%</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">。随着苹果智能覆盖度逐渐增加，苹果不得不在外部求解，由于此前已与谷歌官宣围绕Gemini展开合作，“云上谷歌”就成了备选之一。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">一家以掌控核心技术和用户体验著称的公司，为什么在最关键的AI算力上，一步步走向外部依赖的困境？</span></span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 8px 8px;white-space:normal;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:19px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><mark style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\"></mark><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:20px;\">01&nbsp;</span></span></h2>\n  <h2 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 8px 24px;white-space:normal;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:19px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:20px;\">苹果云“太拉胯”</span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">苹果其实早就开始依赖谷歌了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">年初，苹果就宣布要在产品里用上谷歌的Gemini大模型，可以理解为模型层面已经掉队，现在连运行Siri的机房都想租谷歌的，这也意味着苹果的硬件基础设施也存在短板。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">按理说，苹果有自己的云服务计划。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">2024年的苹果开发者大会，苹果正式推出“苹果智能”服务，深度集成于iPhone等全系列硬件，内置写作工具（改写、校对、摘要）、实时翻译（消息、FaceTime、通话）等能力，基础任务基于端侧模型来处理，复杂任务通过“私有云计算”（Private Cloud Compute）安全调用云端算力。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">不过，根据前员工披露的消息，苹果的“私有云计算”部署进展并不顺利。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">The information援引前员工的消息称，“私有云计算”系统上线后，平均使用率仅10%，且很多服务器并未部署。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">考虑到苹果已经提出了“今年推出的新版Siri能迅速获得用户青睐”的目标，短期内就不得不向外看——寻找第三方算力支持。</span></span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 8px 8px;white-space:normal;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:19px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><mark style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\"></mark><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:20px;\">02&nbsp;</span></span></h2>\n  <h2 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 8px 24px;white-space:normal;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:19px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:20px;\">AI Capex保守的后遗症</span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">苹果自建云这条路，走得磕磕绊绊，根源在于保守的AI资本支出。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在过去几年，当Meta、微软、谷歌、亚马逊疯狂砸钱建数据中心、抢AI芯片，今年几大云厂的主要资本支出预计逼近7000亿美元。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">与之相对的是，苹果一直强调恪守财务纪律，AI基础设施相关的资本支出，2026年预计为130亿美元，增幅只有2%。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.8260416666666667\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"960\" style=\"margin-top:0px;padding:0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;border:0px none;width:100%;max-width:100%;border-radius:4px;display:inline-block;aspect-ratio:1.21172 / 1;\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"464\" data-imgfileid=\"544081696\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7403d366&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FQmK3dYQtkw2LGQ2icpwzDzZWVmSNzGe9E3RM9lc7V17bC96OLvgMEO2bxbiaibb9Wq9tichTbhOB3icvoqm45yPJd5Nv1QvLOS35UfMcClGYLewc%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">按照1GW容量数据中心预计500亿美元来推算，苹果的130亿美元全部投入到基础设施时，2026年只能兑现260兆瓦的数据中心。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这种级别对于一个单季度营收超过千亿美元的巨头来说，显得过于“吝啬”和保守。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">The Information援引多位前苹果高管和工程师的消息，称基础设施项目在内部频繁遇到“阻挠”，但凡有想把苹果的云基础设施做大做强的项目，最后都会被财务部门卡住。理由是：</span></span><strong style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;font-weight: bolder;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">现有的服务器都没用满，为什么还要花钱建新的？</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">据了解，2013年，苹果内部团队就想整合服务器资源，搭建一个类似谷歌那样所有部门都能用的共享“资源池”，结果项目负责人、时任工程总监帕特里克·盖茨（Patrick Gates）因为推不动，几年后离职了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">2019年，苹果从推特挖来技术高管迈克·阿博特（Mike Abbott），后者也想继续推动“公共算力池”，还推动了“ACDC项目”立项，把苹果自研芯片用到数据中心里，并且考虑过以后像亚马逊那样对外出租算力。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">据悉，该项目得到了芯片负责人约翰尼·斯鲁吉（Johny Srouji）等高层的支持，但最终因为财务部门的“拦截”导致项目迟迟无法落地。2023年，阿博特出走通用汽车，他带领的一批云专家也跟着离开了苹果。</span></span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 8px 8px;white-space:normal;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:19px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><mark style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\"></mark><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:20px;\">03&nbsp;</span></span></h2>\n  <h2 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 8px 24px;white-space:normal;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:19px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:20px;\">部门墙致苹果云“营养不良”</span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">苹果云搞不起来，钱是一个问题，“文化”是另一个问题。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">曾在谷歌干过十几年、后来又在苹果参与下一代Siri开发的技术人员伊格尔·纳维尔纽克（Igor Naverniouk）的观点是文化差异。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">“苹果和谷歌的工程文化，完全是两码事。”</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">伊格尔表示，在谷歌，所有工程师都共享一套集中式的超级计算机，资源是打通的，用起来很方便。但在苹果，各部门就像一个个独立的小王国，有自己的技术选型和服务器，相互之间高筑“部门墙”。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">The Information援引前苹果工程师的话称，部门间的隔阂，导致了一种现象——当年iTunes的服务器有空余算力，其他部门却用不了，需要从外部租云服务。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这种“各自为政”部门体系，不仅浪费钱，也让苹果的云服务变得很“笨重”，想集中力量推一个新项目，往往要协调很长时间，而在谷歌内部，早就把云服务做成了一个标准化的产品，安全、稳定、按需使用。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这恰恰解释了为什么苹果最终“妥协”了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">据知情人士透露，苹果软件主管、隐私问题“一把手”，高级副总裁克雷格·费德里吉（Craig Federighi）一度因数据安全顾虑，多年禁止工程师使用谷歌云，但在2023年谷歌升级安全系统后，苹果也调整策略，迅速拥抱了对方。</span></span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 8px 8px;white-space:normal;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:19px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><mark style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\"></mark><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:20px;\">04&nbsp;</span></span></h2>\n  <h2 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 8px 24px;white-space:normal;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:19px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:20px;\">自研ASIC还在路上</span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">苹果通过iPhone等产品证明了自研SoC的水平和性能，但这并不能与数据中心场景下好用画等号。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">2024年，知名分析机构Semianalysis曾经披露过一则信息，称苹果大量增产用于高端Mac Studio和Mac Pro产品线的M2 Ultra芯片，但该产品线并未进行实质性的更新。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">产品线没更新，增量的M2 Ultra芯片用往何处？苹果的数据中心。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这一推测也印证了The information的报道，其援引前苹果云工程师和AI员工的观点，称为“私有云计算”准备的苹果芯片，本来就不是专门为AI训练和推理设计，用来跑谷歌Gemini那样的大模型，效果并不好，给这些服务器更新软件，也比普通服务器麻烦得多、慢得多。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">要解决上述问题，短期内苹果的解决方案只有一个，背靠谷歌云这样的第三方合作伙伴，长期仍然依赖自研ASIC芯片。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">根据我们掌握的消息，苹果自研AI芯片的进展节奏相对较慢，其AI ASIC芯片Baltra由博通负责高速互联，SerDes IP以及后段布线，预计2026年上半年进入流片阶段，最快2028年可以量产，且部署仍需要时间。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">不过，根据知名分析师郭明錤的预判，苹果自研AI芯片的进展有可能相对提前，自2026年开始量产，并且于2026下半年量产，2027年开始部署并在同年底上线。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">实际上，苹果也在推动相关的部署。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">2025年2月，苹果就开始推动制造回流，并宣布了一项为期四年、投资5000亿美元的美国制造业发展计划，该计划预计将创造2万个新的美国就业岗位，这其中就包含了在德州的数据中心服务器制造业务。</span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "揭示苹果因自建云基础设施（PCC）利用率低、AI 资本支出保守及内部部门墙等问题，被迫考虑将新版 Siri 托管至谷歌云的现状与深层原因。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "揭示苹果因自建云基础设施（PCC）利用率低、AI 资本支出保守及内部部门墙等问题，被迫考虑将新版 Siri 托管至谷歌云的现状与深层原因。",
  "summary": "文章深入探讨了苹果在 AI 算力基础设施建设上面临的严峻困境。尽管苹果此前高调推出“私有云计算”（PCC）以强调隐私安全，但据内部消息显示，该系统上线后利用率仅为 10%，且大量服务器处于闲置状态。造成这一局面的根源在于苹果长期奉行的保守财务纪律，其 AI 资本支出远低于微软、谷歌等竞争对手。此外，苹果内部严重的“部门墙”文化导致算力资源无法共享，且目前使用的 M2 Ultra 芯片在 AI 推理效率上不及预期。由于自研 AI ASIC 芯片最快也要到 2026 年后才能量产，苹果在短期内不得不打破“隐私禁忌”，寻求将核心产品 Siri 的算力需求托管至谷歌云，反映了其在 AI 转型中的阵痛。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "苹果私有云计算（PCC）利用率极低，被迫寻求谷歌云的外部算力支持。",
      "explanation": "尽管苹果强调隐私与自研，但 PCC 上线后平均使用率仅 10%，面对新版 Siri 带来的巨大算力需求，苹果在短期内无法通过自有设施满足，只能向合作伙伴谷歌寻求机房托管方案。"
    },
    {
      "point": "苹果长期奉行的保守财务纪律，成为其 AI 基础设施建设滞后的核心根源。",
      "explanation": "相比微软、谷歌等巨头数千亿美元的投入，苹果 2026 年 AI 资本支出预计仅 130 亿美元。财务部门常以现有资源未用满为由拦截扩建项目，导致苹果在算力竞赛中错失先机。"
    },
    {
      "point": "苹果内部严重的“部门墙”文化，阻碍了算力资源的标准化整合与高效利用。",
      "explanation": "苹果各部门如同独立王国，拥有各自的技术选型和服务器，缺乏统一的资源池。这种“各自为政”的模式不仅造成了资源浪费，也让云服务的标准化和快速迭代变得异常困难。"
    },
    {
      "point": "现有服务器芯片在 AI 任务上适配性不足，且自研 AI ASIC 芯片量产尚需时日。",
      "explanation": "苹果目前将 M2 Ultra 芯片用于数据中心，但其并非专为 AI 训练和推理设计，效率有限。而代号为 Baltra 的自研 AI 芯片预计最快 2026 年量产，远水难救近火。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "苹果可能要把最核心产品之一的 Siri，送到谷歌数据中心'寄养'了。",
